title: Episode 26: Tito Bobby-Honeyboy

description:
Bobby gets contact high from Coco.

Khalyla gives great advice to a 14 year old girl about meth.

Gilbert is Dr. Nothing.

Gilbert apologizes to Ate and Appa.

We go over the Filipino naming system, the great traits of Lucifer, and why Asians aren't fond of the EBT card.

 

Recorded January 25, 2016

Music by Bobby Lee
